#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Making your Choice"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now that your kernel is configured and compiled and the necessary system\n"
"configuration files are filled in correctly, it is time to install a\n"
"program that will fire up your kernel when you start the system. Such a\n"
"program is called a <e>bootloader</e>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installing the SPARC Bootloader: SILO"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"It is now time to install and configure <uri\n"
"link=\"http://www.sparc-boot.org\">SILO</uri>, the Sparc Improved boot\n"
"LOader.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installing SILO"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>emerge silo</i>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now open up your favorite editor (we use <c>nano</c> as an example) and\n"
"create <path>/etc/silo.conf</path>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Creating /etc/silo.conf"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>nano -w /etc/silo.conf</i>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:54
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Below you'll find an example <path>silo.conf</path> file. It uses the\n"
"partitioning scheme we use throughout this book and\n"
"<path>kernel-<keyval id=\"kernel-version\"/></path> as kernelimage.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example /etc/silo.conf"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"partition = 1         <comment># Boot partition (= root partition)</comment>\n"
"root = /dev/sda1      <comment># Root partition</comment>\n"
"timeout = 150         <comment># Wait 15 seconds before booting the default section</comment>\n"
"\n"
"image = /boot/kernel-<keyval id=\"kernel-version\"/>\n"
"  label = linux\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:69
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you use the example <path>silo.conf</path> delivered by Portage, be\n"
"sure to comment out <e>all</e> lines that you do not need.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:74
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If the physical disk on which you want to install SILO (as bootloader) differs\n"
"from the physical disk on which <path>/etc/silo.conf</path> resides, you must\n"
"copy over <path>/etc/silo.conf</path> to a partition on that disk. Assuming that\n"
"<path>/boot</path> is a separate partition on that disk, copy over the\n"
"configuration file to <path>/boot</path> and run <c>/sbin/silo -f</c>:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Only if /boot and the SILO destination are not on the same disk"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:82
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>cp /etc/silo.conf /boot</i>\n"
"# <i>/sbin/silo -f -C /boot/silo.conf</i>\n"
"/boot/silo.conf appears to be valid\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "Otherwise just run <c>/sbin/silo -f</c>:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "Run silo"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:92
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>/sbin/silo -f</i>\n"
"/etc/silo.conf appears to be valid\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><note>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:97
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You have to run <c>silo</c> (with parameters) again each time you update or\n"
"reinstall the <c>sys-boot/silo</c> package.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now continue with <uri link=\"#reboot\">Rebooting the System</uri>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "Rebooting the System"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:113
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Exit the chrooted environment and unmount all mounted partitions. Then type in \n"
"that one magical command you have been waiting for: <c>reboot</c>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "Exiting the chroot, unmounting all partitions and rebooting"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:118
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>exit</i>\n"
"cdimage ~# <i>cd</i>\n"
"cdimage ~# <i>umount /mnt/gentoo/boot /mnt/gentoo/dev /mnt/gentoo/proc /mnt/gentoo</i>\n"
"cdimage ~# <i>reboot</i>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:125
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Of course, don't forget to remove the bootable CD, otherwise the CD will be\n"
"booted again instead of your new Gentoo system.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/2008.0/hb-install-sparc-bootloader.xml:130
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Once rebooted in your Gentoo installation, finish up with <uri\n"
"link=\"?part=1&amp;chap=11\">Finalizing your Gentoo Installation</uri>.\n"
msgstr ""
